#: src-en/data/events_ships.xml.append:7
msgid ""
"data/events_ships.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RK_BAM_EXIT_BOSS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship is destroyed. The other gatekeepers give a solemn nod. \"Whoever "
"passed our coordinates along to you made a good choice, and so did you "
"coming here. You are free to go! Have some free repairs too.\""

#: src-en/data/events_ships.xml.append:13
msgid ""
"data/events_ships.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RK_BAM_EXIT_BOSS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Now that you've passed the test, the other gatekeepers allow you out of the "
"sector, and hint that since you even managed to leave the ship in one piece,"
" you get a free random deckhand!"

